96
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:42,640
Under the relevant provisions of

97
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,680
the Criminal Procedure Law,

98
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,320
the general situation where an appellant dies...

99
