112
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,440
We request to call the witness,

113
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,560
Liu Acui, to the stand.

114
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,760
She owns the barbecue restaurant

115
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,240
