121
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,600
No objection, Your Honor.

122
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:30,240
Allow the witness to take the stand.

123
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:02,320
What's wrong?

124
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:04,360
