130
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,760
That day was pure chaos.

131
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,200
I…I…I…

132
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,040
I just saw a man

133
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,200
