160
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,800
He must be held criminally liable

161
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,440
in accordance with the law.

162
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,040
Does the appellant

163
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,400
