184
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,040
Clerk of the court, please proceed.

185
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:50,800
Let me go!

186
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,120
Beat him to death!

187
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:54,680
