190
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,720
Based on the footage,

191
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,880
it's clear that

192
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,680
Zhao Dong was inflicting harm on

193
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:14,720
