882
00:44:00,040 --> 00:44:01,800
If such an act can be forgiven,

883
00:44:01,920 --> 00:44:03,920
how can we face our fellow lawyers?

884
00:44:04,040 --> 00:44:04,840
Nor can we

885
00:44:04,840 --> 00:44:06,080
