902
00:44:42,560 --> 00:44:43,920
Hi. Come this way, please.

903
00:44:43,920 --> 00:44:44,560
Okay.

904
00:44:44,680 --> 00:44:46,080
Mr. Fang asked me to handle

905
00:44:46,080 --> 00:44:47,200
