914
00:44:57,080 --> 00:44:57,880
The boy and girl winners,

915
00:44:57,880 --> 00:44:59,080
they will

916
00:44:59,080 --> 00:45:00,040
represent our school

917
00:45:00,040 --> 00:45:00,880
to shoot

918
00:45:00,880 --> 00:45:02,640
